                <zone fixed-size='665' forceUpdate='true' h='35625' hidden-by-user='true' id='149' type-v2='text' w='55417' x='16917' y='51500'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>The dashboard identifies the </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>strongest opportunities for future growth</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>. It highlights expanding product categories, seasonal demand patterns, and store-level improvement opportunities that could increase revenue and profitability.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>How to Read This Dashboard</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>• KPI cards summarize potential revenue upside and the fastest-growing category.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>• Category Revenue Growth compares year-over-year performance across major product categories.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>• Fastest Growing Subcategories highlights the product segments driving growth.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>• Seasonal Demand by Category reveals peak demand periods throughout the year.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>• Store Margin Opportunities identifies stores with the greatest potential for profitability improvement.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#6f3132'>____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#6f3132' fontsize='11'>★ </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>Use this dashboard to prioritize growth initiatives, allocate resources to high-potential areas, and target stores with the largest opportunity for performance improvement.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='15' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#faf9f6db' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
