                <zone fixed-size='665' forceUpdate='true' h='35625' hidden-by-user='true' id='142' type-v2='text' w='55417' x='16917' y='51500'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>The dashboard investigates the </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>factors reducing profitability across the business</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>. It focuses on the impact of discounting, production costs, and low-margin product segments to identify where profit is being eroded.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>How to Read The Dashboard</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>• KPI cards highlight the total impact of discounting and the lowest-margin product category.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>• Profit Margin Bridge shows how revenue is reduced by discounts and production costs before reaching gross profit.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>• Discount Impact on Profit Margin trend examines the relationship between discounting and profitability over time.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>• Product Cost vs Selling Price compares production costs against selling prices across subcategories.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>• Lowest Margin Subcategories identifies the weakest-performing product segments based on margin performance.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#6f3132'>____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#6f3132' fontsize='11'>★ </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>Use this dashboard to pinpoint margin pressure areas, then navigate to </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#6f3132' underline='true'>Growth Opportunities </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>to identify where future revenue and profit expansion can be achieved.</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#ffffff'>.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='15' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#faf9f6db' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='4250' id='67' type-v2='text' w='42500' x='16917' y='57875'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#9d7660' fontsize='11'>Production Cost</run>
                    <run fontsize='11'>Æ </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#898989' fontsize='11'>vs</run>
                    <run fontsize='11'>Æ </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#a89a8c' fontsize='11'>Selling Price</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
