                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#333333' fontsize='10'>Philea&apos;s overall business performance</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000'>, </run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333'>combining revenue, profitability, and store-level results into a single view.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#333333' fontsize='10'>How to Read The Dashboard</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000'>• </run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333'>KPI cards summarize overall revenue,  gorss profit, margin, and growth performance.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333'>• Revenue &amp; Profit Trend highlights monthly performance patterns and profitability trends.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333'>• Profit Margin by Country &amp; Category heatmap reveals the strongest and weakest market-category combinations.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333'>• Top and Bottom Performing Stores compare store-level revenue performance and margin contribution.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333'>• Store Performance Matrix classifies stores using average revenue and average profit margin benchmarks to identify star performers, hidden gems, margin pressure stores, and underperformers.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#6f3132'>____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#6f3132' fontsize='11'>★ </run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333'>Use this dashboard to identify performance strengths or concerns, then navigate to </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#6f3132' underline='true'>Margin Drivers</run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333'> for profitability analysis or </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#6f3132' underline='true'>Growth Opportunities</run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333'> to explore expansion potential.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#ffffff'>.</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='15' />
                <format attr='margin' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin-right' value='0' />
                <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                <format attr='padding-right' value='10' />
                <format attr='padding-left' value='10' />
                <format attr='background-color' value='#faf9f6db' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
